properties.headline: CHANGED TRAFFIC CONDITIONS - SURRY HILLS Chalmers St between Cleveland St and Eddy Ave
properties.otherAdvice:
A Special Event Clearway will be in operation on the western side of Chalmers Street from 2am Saturday 27 September until 2am Monday 29 September.
The taxi zone will be moved to the eastern side of Chalmers Street (adjacent to the dental hospital).
Please check signage as vehicles will be towed from the Special Event Clearway and fines apply.
